### WorkOrder CRUD API Tests

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000/api/WorkOrders
@authToken = your-jwt-token-here

### Get all work orders (with pagination and filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10&searchTerm=&status=&priority=&assignedTechnicianId=&workOrderTypeId=&scheduledDateFrom=&scheduledDateTo=&sortBy=CreatedAt&sortDescending=true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get work order by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Create a new work order
POST {{baseUrl}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customer": "John Doe",
  "customerContact": "john.doe@email.com",
  "type": "MeterInstallation",
  "priority": "High",
